  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p><ul><li>Sales of Pharmaceutical products (GPs & Hospitals)</li><li>Prospect and build new customer base on achieve sales targets.</li><li>Build rapport with customers.</li><li>Perform specific customer and market survey.</li></ul><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Minimum 'O' level to Diploma holders in any discipline</li><li>Fresh Diploma holders may apply</li><li>Possess excellent communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Professional sales etiquettes</li><li>Good planning and organizing skills</li><li>Possess drive, resourceful & dedicated</li><li>Must be independent but also works well in a team</li><li>Possess own transport is a must</li><li>Possess own transport</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred Qualifications</strong>:</p><ul><li>Experience in the pharmaceuticals industry relevant to the company</li><li>Familiarity with the local market and customer preferences</li></ul><p>Benefit</p><ul><li>Attractive commission achievable</li><li>Incentives given when sales target are exceeded</li></ul>",
